<h1 className={"openapi__heading"}>GetWhiteboardUserAuth</h1>

<MethodEndpoint method={"get"} path={"/"}></MethodEndpoint>


Call this API to query users' whiteboard permissions. A maximum of 10 users can be queried at a time.
If no permissions have been set for a queried user, the server will not return that user's permission data.

<Note title="Note">Rate limit\: 50 requests/second (Test environment\: 1 request/second).</Note>
